    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Wolf Pack",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Though wolf packs can be a menace to farming communities that rely on livestock, they prefer not to go after humanoids or other dangerous foes. However, hungry packs don't have the luxury of being cautious.",
